thread.title: Iran: EU support of nuclear deal isn't enough

title: Iran: EU support of nuclear deal isn't enough
text:
Iran: EU support of nuclear deal isn't enough 1:06pm BST - 01:27
Iran's foreign ministry says that Washington's withdrawal from the nuclear agreement means Tehran doesn't have enough benefits to uphold their side of the deal, even with the remaining European powers still on board. Matthew Larotonda reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
